### Health
GET {{host}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

### Info
GET {{host}}/actuator/info
Accept: application/json

### Metrics index
GET {{host}}/actuator/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Specific metric — JVM memory used
GET {{host}}/actuator/metrics/jvm.memory.used
Accept: application/json

### Specific metric — cache gets (Redis hits/misses)
GET {{host}}/actuator/metrics/cache.gets
Accept: application/json
